OL,3,CParents of SEND children facing debt
OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,FParents say they are struggling to
OL,7,Fsupport their children with special
OL,8,Feducational needs, due to the 'broken'
OL,9,Fsystem, ITV News Social Affairs
OL,10,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker reports
OL,12,FA coalition of charities has told ITV
OL,13,FNews that parents of children with
OL,14,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,15,Fdisabilities (SEND) are being pushed
OL,16,Fto the brink by a broken system and
OL,17,Fleft with no choice but to give up
OL,18,Ftheir employment to advocate for their
OL,19,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
