OL,3,CParents of SEND children facing debt
OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,FParents and carers have warned they
OL,7,Fare increasingly being "forced" to
OL,8,Fquit their jobs, reduce their hours or
OL,9,Ftake out loans, as overstretched and
OL,10,Funder-resourced schools struggle to
OL,11,Fsupport students with additional needs.
OL,13,FIt comes as the government's widely
OL,14,Fanticipated - and long-delayed -
OL,15,FSchools White Paper is expected to be
OL,16,Fpublished next week, laying out plans
OL,17,Ffor systemic SEND reforms with a focus
OL,18,Fon making mainstream schools more
OL,19,Finclusive.
