OL,3,CParents of SEND children facing debt
OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,FKertisha Larmond's five-year-old son
OL,7,FTheo has severe autism and gets
OL,8,Fspecialist support, but it has been a
OL,9,Fbattle every step of the way.
OL,11,FThe mother of two has to pay out for
OL,12,Fspecialist equipment and language
OL,13,Fsupport, and has had to cut her hours
OL,14,Fat work to care for him, which has
OL,15,Ftaken a toll on her mental health as
OL,16,Fwell as her finances.
OL,18,FMs Larmond, from London, worked as a
OL,19,Fhairdresser for 15 years, but had to
OL,20,Fquit to look after her son. A decision
OL,21,Fshe said "broke my heart".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
