OL,3,CParents of SEND children facing debt
OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,F"I feel like I lost a part of me when
OL,7,FI left that job," Ms Larmond told ITV
OL,8,FNews.
OL,10,F"When I was in work, I felt like that
OL,11,Fwas my little escape from what was
OL,12,Freally going on. You put your mask on
OL,13,Fand you go to work."
OL,15,FMs Larmond continues to do some
OL,16,Fhairdressing work from home to give
OL,17,Fher the flexibility to care for Theo,
OL,18,Fbut this has left her financially
OL,19,Fstruggling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
