OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,F"You just do what you have to do, and
OL,7,Fjuggle everything, but it's hard," she
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"As a mum I've always felt like,
OL,11,Ffinancially am I failing? Because I
OL,12,Fwant to be able to get what he
OL,13,Fdeserves and I should be able to give
OL,14,Fthat.
OL,16,F"I thought when I got the diagnosis,
OL,17,Fall this help would come, which is
OL,18,Fsilly now I look back because the
OL,19,Fdiagnosis doesn't really change much."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
