OL,6,FMs Larmond is not alone in her
OL,7,Fexperience.
OL,9,FA survey shared exclusively with ITV
OL,10,FNews by the Disabled Children's
OL,11,FPartnership found that over a third
OL,12,F(37%) of parents and carers in England
OL,13,Fhave had to quit their job to support
OL,14,Fa child with SEND, while 34% have had
OL,15,Fto reduce their working hours and
OL,16,Faround a quarter (22%) have had to
OL,17,Fchange jobs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
