OL,3,CParents of SEND children facing debt
OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 31% of the families
OL,7,Fsurveyed said they have to rely on
OL,8,Fbenefits due to the financial pressure
OL,9,Fof supporting a child with additional
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,FAnna Bird, from the DCP, said it is a
OL,13,F"stain on society" that a generation
OL,14,Fof children has been "let down by the
OL,15,Fsystem that has insufficient support".
OL,17,FOver a quarter (27%) of parents and
OL,18,Fcarers surveyed by the DCP said they
OL,19,Fdo not feel their child is safe at
OL,20,Fschool due to the level of support
OL,21,Fthey receive.
