OL,6,FAnna Bird, from the Disabled
OL,7,FChildren's Partnership, told ITV News
OL,8,Fit is a 'stain on our society' that
OL,9,Fchildren with SEND are not being
OL,10,Fproperly supported in the classroom
OL,12,FThe data also found that a quarter of
OL,13,Fchildren are missing about four weeks
OL,14,Fof school education, while one in
OL,15,Feight children are missing two-thirds
OL,16,Fof the academic year, leaving the
OL,17,Fparents and carers to fill in the gaps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
