OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,F"They are not able to live a rich
OL,7,Ffamily life, and that is a stain on
OL,8,Four society and something that the
OL,9,Fgovernment absolutely has to grasp,"
OL,10,FMs Bird told ITV News.
OL,12,F"Too many children are just not being
OL,13,Fsupported in the classroom. Children
OL,14,Fwith SEND who need some adjustments to
OL,15,Fthe school day and extra support in
OL,16,Fthe classroom are just not getting it,
OL,17,Fand so are missing out on being in
OL,18,Fschool by not being able to attend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
