OL,6,FHe is now back at school but is still
OL,7,Fstruggling. He was suspended seven
OL,8,Ftimes last year, and can only attend a
OL,9,Ffew hours a day, a situation that has
OL,10,Fmeant his mother has had to stop
OL,11,Fworking.
OL,13,FMs Ellis told ITV News that dealing
OL,14,Fwith the current SEND system has been
OL,15,Fa "nightmare".
OL,17,FLucas is still waiting for a space at
OL,18,Fa specialist unit that can meet his
OL,19,Fneeds, and his mother is worried he is
OL,20,Fnot receiving the support he is
OL,21,Fentitled to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
