OL,4,Cand 'forced' to give up work
OL,6,F"They've got to pay for someone to
OL,7,Fcome in to school to be that one-to-
OL,8,Fone," Ms Ellis said.
OL,10,F"Even though he's getting the highest
OL,11,Flevel of funding, it still doesn't
OL,12,Fcover what they need for him. I'm just
OL,13,Fworried for his future," she added.
OL,15,FConcerns have been raised by parents
OL,16,Fover changes to education, health and
OL,17,Fcare plans (EHCP), a legal document
OL,18,Fthat details children's support.
