OL,6,FMs Martin, who is neurodivergent
OL,7,Fherself, has three daughters, aged 12,
OL,8,Feight and three, who all have
OL,9,Fadditional needs.
OL,11,F"It almost seems as though what they
OL,12,Fare putting in place might stand to
OL,13,Fexacerbate the issues that we
OL,14,Fcurrently have," she told ITV News.
OL,16,F"All we have actually asked for is
OL,17,Fthat there is better adherence to the
OL,18,Flaws by local authority and that local
OL,19,Fauthorities are held to account and
OL,20,Fthat there is a push to moving towards
OL,21,Fwhat SEND inclusion looks like."
