OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fsaid last month that increased
OL,8,Finvestment was key to tackling the
OL,9,Fcrisis, announcing a #200 million
OL,10,Finvestment in teaching training, aimed
OL,11,Fat equipping staff across nurseries,
OL,12,Fschools and colleges with the tools to
OL,13,Fsupport pupils with SEND.
OL,15,FThis followed the government's pledge
OL,16,Flast year to invest #3 billion across
OL,17,Fthree years in order to create more
OL,18,Fthan 60,000 new specialist places in
OL,19,Fmainstream schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
