OL,6,FA Department for Education
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "For too long,
OL,8,Ffamilies have been forced to fight for
OL,9,Fsupport that should be routinely
OL,10,Favailable when and where it is needed.
OL,11,FOur Schools White Paper will be a once-
OL,12,Fin-a-generation change to children's
OL,13,Flives for the better, ending the one-
OL,14,Fsize-fits-all school system that has
OL,15,Ffailed too many children and families.
