OL,6,F"We're already laying the foundations
OL,7,Fof a truly inclusive system, investing
OL,8,Fbillions in tens of thousands of new
OL,9,Fplaces that meet the needs of children
OL,10,Fwith SEND and training up every
OL,11,Fteacher and teaching assistant in line
OL,12,Fwith the best practice across the
OL,13,Fcountry.
OL,15,F"Our reforms will create a better
OL,16,Fsystem for all families, where support
OL,17,Fis delivered earlier and closer to
OL,18,Fhome, while retaining legal rights to
OL,19,Fsupport."
